{% block title %} About {% endblock %}
{% block body %}
		<div class="table-responsive">
			<table class="table" id="about">
				<thead>
					<tr>
						<th scope="col" class="text-center font-weight-bold">Here is the assignment as discussed.</th>
					</tr>
				</thead>
				<tbody>
						<tr>
						  <td scope="row">Build a basic Create, read, delete and update application using Symphony4, html, css and mysql with the following functionalities:-</td>
						</tr>
							<td>
								<ul>
									<li>
										Create a product page which will enable a user to input some basic details like product name, product price, stock available, status (Dropdown with values In Stock, Out of Stock, Pre Order), Category( Dropdown form already added categories form category table.)
									</li>
									<li>
										Create another page called Category page where user can create new categories.
									</li>
