										<b>Cascade delete functionality is there if you delete a category all related product will be deleted.</b>
									</li>
									<li>
										<b>
											You can Add and View Products and category by browsing through menu.
										</b>
									</li>
									<li>
										<b>
											You can show, edit and delete records form the list of categories and products.
										</b>
									</li>
									<li>
										You don't have to create the authentication module and anyone can use it if they have a url.
									</li>
									<li>
										Regarding UI just create a basic UI using bootstrap HTML or whatever suits (UI will not be evaluated)
									</li>
								</ul>
